    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>&quot;In the dark Cursed abandoned Mansion, and the witch is looking for answer&quot;</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The new DLC for Cursed Mansion, with the spirit of adventure and unknown curse, explore the mansion with the new &quot;Witch Outfit&quot;. Nobody will know what will happen when the the witch is lurking in the spooky mansion, will the spirit of the undead guide her to her destiny?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>DLC Game Walkthrough:</i></strong><br>1. After purchasing a DLC costume, you can now gain access to several special mirrors scattered inside the mansion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. When you go inside one, you will find treasure chest with the costume inside it for you to claim</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. After you claimed one, open the inventory to equip any costume you want to use throughout your journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. You have now wore the costume and ready to explore the mansion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras/0044004cb1b3dfa3c84e6972d306af09.avif?t=1739865333\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras_big/0044004cb1b3dfa3c84e6972d306af09.avif?t=1739865333 width=800 height=800 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras/4d35eb1c63c2f9b7fc77ff60e7234a0e.avif?t=1739865333\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras_big/4d35eb1c63c2f9b7fc77ff60e7234a0e.avif?t=1739865333 width=800 height=800 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras/2e612539206b686f3dbad578ae84c0b2.avif?t=1739865333\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras_big/2e612539206b686f3dbad578ae84c0b2.avif?t=1739865333 width=800 height=800 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras/2e5e8e54308d16a3fad917ed6e3b7cde.avif?t=1739865333\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294850/extras_big/2e5e8e54308d16a3fad917ed6e3b7cde.avif?t=1739865333 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;See you in the Mansion, Kind Spirit&quot;</i></p>",
